{
  "texts": [
    "All activity with intensities 1 MET (1 Met = 3.5 ml/kg/ min) or higher was calculated on wear time.",
    "Patients with at least four valid days (3 weekdays and 1 weekend day) were included in the analyses (monitor wear time of ≥ 600 min/ day) (Prince et al. 2015).",
    "All measurements were taken at the beginning and completion of 18 sessions of community-based exercise CR programs.",
    "The protocols of pre-and post-intervention were the same for each patient.",
    "Compliance and adherence to exercise training was determined by recording the number of sessions attended."
  ]
}